title: Multi-Stage Attack: C2, Lateral Movement, and Data Exfiltration
summary: Detected multi-stage attack spanning 5 phases: initial compromise, C2 establishment, lateral movement, data exfiltration, web exploitation. Affected 4 hosts. Attack originated from workstation-042 and spread to critical servers including server-db-01. Data exfiltration detected via both C2 channel and DNS tunneling.
